    "    Using current S&P 500 list excludes delisted/removed stocks (losers)\n",
    "    and includes newly-added stocks (winners).\n",
    "    This inflates backtest returns by ~5-15%.\n",
    "    \n",
    "    Solution: Use point-in-time S&P 500 constituents from alternate sources.\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    print(\"\\n\" + \"=\"*70)\n",
    "    print(\"SURVIVORSHIP BIAS FIX: Using point-in-time constituents\")\n",
    "    print(\"=\"*70)\n",
