    "## Section 10 (continued): Defense Contractor Contract Awards Signal\n",
    "\n",
    "**Optional Bonus:** Government procurement data as leading indicator of future revenue. \n",
    "Uses SAM.gov contract awards data (3-6 month lag before revenue recognition).\n",
    "Expected IC: 0.02-0.03 (orthogonal to LLM sentiment)"
   ]
